{"tid":40832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真問 ex 生日應該送咩禮物好","createTime":"2016-12-15T12:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T12:55:31.000Z","uid":66068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a423e4bfa4384f3f75ebb8b792ba9d707ee4fb9d","tid":40832,"uid":66068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:39:44.000Z","msg":"同ex分手一年多, 但分手後做得返朋友(唔係兵). 佢生日應該送咩好."},{"pid":"e44b41411d9440d72c85fdd9abd03619d9828e5c","tid":40832,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"投其所好"},{"pid":"1aff2a4a62f24bfb2f2b0b720dcff1507f96aba9","tid":40832,"uid":3502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"我邀你老母共進餐"},{"pid":"f0e03bad6083e61205e7b24b865c0ea3a170b67d","tid":40832,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a25a48f1185d9a0babc2327a97f1ec48ea7b71","tid":40832,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:52:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed31b4a2c3da28a5c5e30ba2791f64da216e0d64","tid":40832,"uid":1577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"送個dom比佢囉<br />\n等佢同其他男人玩得開心又放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}